      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Hard to knock the form of BORROWED TIME (3) having won the last two times he raced at this circuit and distance with a Menangle placing in between. Worked to the front from a couple of spots wider before scoring by 1.3m last week so can take advantage of the lower draw. WISHAS DARLING NZ (5) is a promising gelding who has won his two starts to date, both at this circuit and distance. Worked from this barrier to find the front before digging deep to score last week. Has upside and could maintain the perfect record. JEWEL MISTRESS (1) has placed in her last three outings at this circuit and distance and the ace draw could see her competitive again. STAY STYLISH (2) improved when runner-up to BORROWED TIME last week and should not have any excuses from the favourable draw.",
